sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User MERGE
    participant D as Delta
    participant F as Storage
    U->>D: merge(source, "t.id = s.id")
    D->>F: Scan target with join predicate
    F-->>D: candidate files (with min/max for skip)
    D->>D: Join source with candidate files
    D->>D: Classify rows: matched / not-matched / not-matched-by-source
    D->>F: Rewrite each affected file with merged rows
    Note over D,F: Whole files are rewritten,<br/>not individual rows
    D->>F: Compute (add, remove) action set
    D->>F: Atomically commit new log entry
    F-->>U: success<br/>operationMetrics: numUpdated, numInserted, numDeleted
